premise_source_doc_sentence: `` Uptown Funk ''  (  stylised as `` UpTown Funk ! ''  )

On November 10 , 2014 , Mark Ronson released the single `` Uptown Funk '' which featured Mars ' vocals and was produced by Ronson , Jeff Bhasker and Mars , included on Ronson 's album Uptown Special  (  2015  )  .

Seven of his singles are among the best-selling singles of all time : in order of release date , `` Just the Way You Are '' , `` Grenade '' , `` The Lazy Song '' , `` Locked Out of Heaven '' , `` When I Was Your Man '' , `` Treasure '' , and `` Uptown Funk '' .
In 2014 , Jamareo recorded with Mark Ronson & Bruno Mars on the biggest song of the 2010s , `` Uptown Funk '' , which lasted at No. 1 on the Hot 100 for 14 weeks .
Artis also appears in the music videos for `` Uptown Funk '' , `` Gorilla '' , and `` Treasure '' with Bruno Mars .
